285
00:20:05,971 --> 00:20:08,639
It'll go up in the air.

286
00:20:08,641 --> 00:20:11,909
And I'll see it,
up there in the mountains.

287
00:20:13,679 --> 00:20:16,480
And I'll come down...

288
00:20:16,482 --> 00:20:19,083
and I'll help you.

289
00:20:19,085 --> 00:20:21,586
You understand?

