00:43:11,388 --> 00:43:13,289
<i>Alpini.</i>

543
00:43:13,291 --> 00:43:15,491
Those bastards.

544
00:43:15,493 --> 00:43:16,693
I'll get my men.

545
00:43:16,695 --> 00:43:17,975
Don't.

