01:09:03,305 --> 01:09:09,210
¶¶ (tense orchestration)

755
01:09:10,446 --> 01:09:11,746
(breathes heavily)

756
01:09:19,421 --> 01:09:22,390
(muttering)

757
01:09:24,627 --> 01:09:26,828
